<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy | DirectFlight.net" description="Privacy Policy for DirectFlight.net — how we collect, use, and protect your information." noindex={true}>
<section class="page-header"><div class="page-header-inner"><div class="page-eyebrow">📄 Legal</div><h1>Privacy Policy</h1><p>Last updated: March 1, 2026</p></div></section>
<div class="policy-wrap">
<div class="policy-meta">Questions about this policy? Email <a href="mailto:hello@directflight.net">hello@directflight.net</a></div>
<p>This Privacy Policy describes how DirectFlight.net ("we," "us," or "our") collects, uses, and shares information about visitors to our website. By using the Site, you agree to the practices described in this policy.</p>
<h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
<h3>Automatically Collected</h3>
<p>When you visit the Site, we automatically collect: IP address and approximate location, browser type and version, operating system, pages visited and time spent, referring URL, and date/time of your visit.</p>
<h3>Voluntarily Provided</h3>
<p>If you submit our contact form or subscribe to email notifications, we collect your name and email address solely to respond to your inquiry or send you requested communications.</p>
<h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
<ul>
<li>Operate and improve the Site and its content</li>
<li>Understand visitor behaviour via aggregate analytics</li>
<li>Deliver relevant advertising through Google AdSense</li>
<li>Respond to inquiries submitted through our contact form</li>
<li>Comply with applicable legal obligations</li>
</ul>
<h2>3. Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h2>
<p>Our Site uses cookies including: <strong>Essential cookies</strong> (required for core functionality), <strong>Analytics cookies</strong> (Google Analytics, aggregated and anonymized), <strong>Advertising cookies</strong> (Google AdSense, interest-based), and <strong>Affiliate tracking cookies</strong> (set by booking partners when you click our links). You can control cookies through your browser settings.</p>
<h2>4. Google AdSense</h2>
<p>We participate in Google AdSense (Publisher ID: ca-pub-3682182847176460). Google uses cookies to serve personalised ads based on your browsing history. You can opt out at <a href="https://adssettings.google.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google's Ads Settings</a>. See <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google's Privacy Policy</a> for more.</p>
<h2>5. Affiliate Links</h2>
<p>We participate in affiliate programs. When you click certain links and make a booking, we may receive a commission at no extra cost to you. Current partners include Skyscanner, Expedia, and Travelpayouts. See our <a href="/affiliate-disclosure">Affiliate Disclosure</a> for full details.</p>
<h2>6. Data Sharing</h2>
<p>We do not sell your personal information. We may share data with: service providers who help operate the Site (under confidentiality obligations); law enforcement when required by law; and successors in the event of a business transfer.</p>
<h2>7. Data Retention</h2>
<p>We retain personal information only as long as necessary. Google Analytics data is retained for 26 months.</p>
<h2>8. Your Rights (PIPEDA)</h2>
<p>Under Canada's PIPEDA, you may access, correct, or withdraw consent to use of your personal information. EEA residents may have additional rights under GDPR. Contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@directflight.net">hello@directflight.net</a> to exercise these rights.</p>
<h2>9. Children's Privacy</h2>
<p>Our Site is not directed at children under 13. If you believe we have inadvertently collected information from a child, please contact us immediately.</p>
<h2>10. Changes</h2>
<p>We may update this policy periodically. The "Last updated" date will reflect any changes. Continued use of the Site constitutes acceptance.</p>
<h2>11. Contact</h2>
<p>Email: <a href="mailto:hello@directflight.net">hello@directflight.net</a> · Jurisdiction: Alberta, Canada</p>
</div>
</BaseLayout>
